Cell["Euclidean space (n = 4)", "Subsection",ExpressionUUID->"98aea49c-d318-4820-9419-9a7f770919c1"],

Cell["\<\
In Euclidean space the metric is the identity and the gamma matrices coincide \
with the flat-space \[CapitalGamma] matrices.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"77a295ef-f056-4b17-a53f-1655f77891cf"],

